com.camerontec.catalys.server.configuration.registry

Class ConfigurationObjectRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.util.configuration.registry.RegistryOfIRegisterables<IRegisterable>
      • com.camerontec.catalys.server.configuration.registry.ConfigurationObjectRegistry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IConfigurationEventListener, IConfigurationEventSource, IObjectRegistry<IRegisterable>

    public class ConfigurationObjectRegistry
extends RegistryOfIRegisterables<IRegisterable>
implements IConfigurationEventListener, IConfigurationEventSource
    Registry of configuration objects within a Catalys Application. This registry represents the properties of components which have been configured but not necessarily loaded into runtime.
